56
00:05:05,238 --> 00:05:06,080
So?

57
00:05:15,281 --> 00:05:18,421
Half a tandoori chicken,
one roomali roti...

58
00:05:18,451 --> 00:05:20,158
Aren't you a South Indian?

59
00:05:20,219 --> 00:05:21,323
Tarn I I ian.

60
00:05:21,721 --> 00:05:22,461
And...

61
