67
00:05:36,269 --> 00:05:38,249
So... coming back
to my question.

68
00:05:39,238 --> 00:05:42,583
What's the difference between
South Indians and Tamilians?

69
00:05:42,675 --> 00:05:43,551
H uge difference.

70
