excites you more...

277
00:17:08,727 --> 00:17:11,230
but I really can't
do anything about it.

278
00:17:12,231 --> 00:17:13,437
Krish!!!

279
00:17:13,732 --> 00:17:16,474
Are you serious?! You're
really not coming with me?

