803
00:50:26,223 --> 00:50:27,463
Hello, sir.

804
00:50:28,091 --> 00:50:29,161
Krish.

805
00:50:31,094 --> 00:50:32,698
Ananya's friend...?

806
00:50:34,031 --> 00:50:35,339
Come... come...

807
00:50:35,399 --> 00:50:36,810
Take off your shoes!

