<i>“These incomyﬂete stories...“</i>

1781
01:57:38,100 --> 01:57:40,842
<i>“And these incomwete goodbyes“</i>

1782
01:57:41,804 --> 01:57:45,843
"Will they remain
incomplete..."

1783
01:57:46,408 --> 01:57:49,617
forever?"

